                    <li>DNS translates names to numbers</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="card card-enhanced">
                <h3>
                    <Icon name="calendar" size={18} class="section-icon" />
                    Wednesday Preview
                </h3>
                <p>Next class we'll dive into writing HTML code and deploying your first website!</p>

                <div class="coming-up">
                    <h4 class="sidebar-subheading">Topics:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>HTML document structure</li>
                        <li>Semantic markup</li>
